  <title>Example applications</title>
  <para>
    Pipes and filters are used quite widely as an architectural solution for 
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem><para>stream-based processing and</para></listitem>
      <listitem><para>
        flexible work flows where work flows can be modified simply by
        rearranging sequences of filters.
        </para></listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </para>
  
  <section>
    <title>Work flow systems</title>
    <para>
       Eterprises have to manage their work flows like, for example, a home loan
       application which has to go through a number of processing steps.
    </para>
  </section>
  
  
  <section>
    <title>Services-oriented architectures</title>
    <para>
