      They receive
    </para>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <title>Unix command framework</title>
    <para>
      The Unix command framework is architected on the pipes and filters architectural pattern.
      It enables one to assemble complex processes by directly feeding the output of one command
      into the input pipe of another.
    </para>
  </section>
  
  <section>
    <title>Compilers</title>
    <para>
      Compiler architecture are often based on the pipes and filters architectural pattern with
      filters performing lexical analysis, parsing,semantic analysis, code generation,
      optimization, linking and so on.
    </para>  
  </section>
  
  
